                    <p class="utterance">Eh. And who lived in the block the gypsies had lived in afterwards?</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Lea</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Yes. In block there lived the gypsies. Or block for gypsies, only gypsies. Why is&#226;gypsies stay, why not Arian, no SS let them live together.</p>
