                    <p class="utterance">Work in the town, with the pickaxe, with the pickaxe, with the shovel. No food, only 150 gram bread every day, noon one liter of water. This way work, eh, 40 hours.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Mh. So, what has happened?</p>
