                                                                                                <b>David Lea</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Deep. There come wagons, every wagon 40 dead. Come together the wagons to the dead. The SS, nonsense. One Jewish wanted do a little (unclear). The SS has not allowed. Have seen comrade, work in the, with the [unintelligible], has said, is my brother, my cousin. Has read a little. No little reading.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">No little what?</p>
