                    <p class="utterance">Camp one, camp two, camp three, camp four, camp five, camp six, camp seven, camp eight, camp nine, camp ten, camp eleven. In camp number four, camp seven, camp seven, there is only quarantine.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
