                                                                                                <b>David Lea</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Quarantine finishes the Jewish with injection. In camp one, there is main, in camp one, it is a camp, work camp. The name is Tannberg. The bad people . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">What is it called? [Interrupting]</p>
