                    <p class="utterance">Yes, have eaten [simultaneously] In camp three. In Bayern. Bayern.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Eh, where was that? In Dachau, in . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Lea</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Not. In Landsberg, Bayern. Camp three.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
